ISLAMABAD, Dec 11 (APP): Minister for Information and Broadcasting Marriyum Aurangzeb on Sunday wished ailing actor Firdous Jamal “good health” and prayed for his speedy recovery.
“My prayers and good wishes are with Firdous Jamal. May the good health attends him!,” she said in a news statement.
